{"tid":2061190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記得上水差D 墜橋手足嗎？ 佢岩岩被判即時還押至8月候審","createTime":"2020-06-12T08:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T16:02:32.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8971ff4d1a5d7a37298b2eb20d8f335352d20f0a","tid":2061190,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官<br />\n#20200527銅鑼灣 #提堂<br />\n<br />\n吳 (22) 🛑自5月27日開始還押至今<br />\n<br />\n控罪：管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2020年5月27日在銅鑼灣東角道及軒尼詩道交界管有兩支鋼筋、一個士巴拿、兩個螺絲批、一個鎚仔、一把刀、一個剪鉗、一個打火機、一個點火器及兩樽天拿水，意圖在無合法辯解下使用該物品，以損壞屬於另一人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n‼️因被告於保釋期間再次被捕，因此即時還押‼️<br />\n<br />\n背景：//吳曾被控管有攻擊性武器罪，於1月5日在上水中心一燈柱旁管有一把生果刀、一枝木棍及一把扳手。據悉，他在去年7月13日曾參與光復上水遊行，被警員追捕時，疑驚慌過度跨越天橋欄杆，險從天橋墮下，幸有人及時拉回。// 香港01<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2020年8月7日1430東區裁判法院再訊，以進行進一步調查。"},{"pid":"5f40c5a724aaf55858018ea6ccb8c3645fbce6e8","tid":2061190,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f139197bc44d896ed7ab127ef68c5cbdc1c4459","tid":2061190,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab23e35e7ef67ca0ec8d3d5341d555e2c4f80f5","tid":2061190,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4e0a35b7ca235b8d7320835aa7bef216f67eaf","tid":2061190,"uid":321048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:19:52.000Z","